WEBVTT

00:29.320 --> 00:29.960
Father.

00:32.240 --> 00:33.700
Haven't I told you before?

00:34.030 --> 00:35.830
Whether in public or in private,

00:35.840 --> 00:37.700
you should just call me "Master."

00:37.880 --> 00:40.140
"Our bodies are gifts from our parents."

00:40.320 --> 00:41.560
This life of mine is

00:41.560 --> 00:43.420
entirely a gift from you, Father.

00:43.880 --> 00:45.150
Had you not taken me in

00:45.390 --> 00:46.960
as your student in Jiankang

00:46.960 --> 00:48.320
and guided me so diligently,

00:48.320 --> 00:50.240
I would never have
reached where I am today.

00:50.240 --> 00:51.350
Everything I believe in and aspire to

00:51.350 --> 00:53.280
has also been nurtured by your teaching.

00:53.280 --> 00:56.010
I would never dare
show you anything but respect.

01:00.840 --> 01:01.600
Good.

01:02.320 --> 01:03.280
My good son.

01:10.950 --> 01:13.150
You are every bit a son of the Xie family.

01:14.710 --> 01:16.840
You've done well these past few years.

01:16.920 --> 01:19.150
You used the reform as a pretext
to reshape the salt and iron monopoly

01:19.150 --> 01:20.310
and clear the waterways.

01:20.310 --> 01:21.870
The people will remember you

01:21.870 --> 01:22.800
and support you.

01:25.480 --> 01:26.950
But the reform

01:27.400 --> 01:30.039
was ultimately initiated by Xiao Wuyi.

01:32.680 --> 01:34.039
If you want to become

01:35.280 --> 01:37.590
the true ruler of the realm,

01:38.039 --> 01:40.920
you must sweep aside

01:43.120 --> 01:44.780
anyone who stands in your way,

01:45.479 --> 01:46.840
one by one, like dust.

03:20.260 --> 03:24.280
[Key to the Phoenix Heart]

03:24.380 --> 03:27.240
[Episode 22]

03:30.280 --> 03:31.190
Xiao Wuyi,

03:32.240 --> 03:34.370
you need to learn to take what you want.

03:45.910 --> 03:48.640
♪ One glance from near stirs my heart ♪

03:48.860 --> 03:51.410
♪ This fleeting moment ♪

03:53.110 --> 03:57.120
♪ Tugs the threads woven by fate ♪

03:54.310 --> 03:55.240
Xiao Wuyi.

03:57.290 --> 03:59.290
♪ Bound tight evermore ♪

03:58.870 --> 03:59.960
Do you hear me?

04:06.360 --> 04:07.120
I hear you.

04:08.590 --> 04:09.280
Good.

04:21.920 --> 04:23.120
You're really drunk.

04:24.680 --> 04:25.510
I'm not.

04:26.600 --> 04:28.660
I still have a New Year's gift for you.

04:38.720 --> 04:39.720
What do you think?

04:44.110 --> 04:48.450
♪ You know my resolve
to live and die together ♪

04:48.470 --> 04:52.130
♪ Believe in my persistence that
I won't run away ♪

04:52.150 --> 04:56.300
♪ You know I'm unyielding ♪

04:57.120 --> 05:00.040
♪ Don't give up or dodge ♪

04:58.290 --> 04:59.050
My red steed.

05:00.640 --> 05:04.410
♪ You know me, seeing things
through from start to finish ♪

05:03.160 --> 05:05.240
My Miraculous Craft
has made a lot of money,

05:04.930 --> 05:09.050
♪ You see my move
under rebellious cover ♪

05:05.240 --> 05:06.560
so I redeemed it.

05:06.680 --> 05:08.110
You're going to the battlefield,

05:08.110 --> 05:09.310
so you need the finest horse.

05:09.310 --> 05:13.300
♪ You know me, I'm willing to be
with you till the end ♪

05:10.750 --> 05:12.270
It can bring you home.

05:13.320 --> 05:17.250
♪ Burn the fire in my heart ♪

05:18.870 --> 05:19.430
Yaoyao.

05:19.640 --> 05:22.410
♪ Sincere hearts remain as of old ♪

05:25.140 --> 05:26.140
I'll do my best...

05:28.800 --> 05:30.600
to spend every New Year with you.

05:59.720 --> 06:01.360
Wait, not this one.

06:02.600 --> 06:04.330
I have a Hetian white jade crown

06:04.720 --> 06:05.850
that Yaoyao gave me.

06:06.870 --> 06:07.560
Today

06:07.800 --> 06:10.130
is the day she'll be officially invested.

06:10.160 --> 06:11.420
I want to wear that one.

06:11.620 --> 06:12.180
Yes.

06:19.880 --> 06:22.320
To Prince Jing'an's Mansion.

06:25.120 --> 06:26.050
Grand Tutor Xie,

06:26.070 --> 06:27.070
have you heard?

06:27.090 --> 06:28.870
Something terrible happened
at the grain canal.

06:28.870 --> 06:30.870
The Xiao family embezzled funds
for the canal.

06:30.870 --> 06:32.390
They replaced river sand
with mud and silt,

06:32.390 --> 06:33.720
causing the grain canal to collapse,

06:33.720 --> 06:35.430
and nearly 100 laborers
were killed or injured.

06:35.430 --> 06:37.630
The County Sheriff has hanged himself.

06:37.720 --> 06:40.650
The outraged crowds
have already reached Jiankang.

06:41.430 --> 06:42.830
There are so many guests today.

06:42.830 --> 06:43.510
Yes.

06:44.830 --> 06:46.310
Congratulations, congratulations.

06:46.310 --> 06:47.170
Please come in.

06:49.070 --> 06:49.920
Why have so many

06:49.920 --> 06:52.240
officials' families come to attend
the ceremony today?

06:52.240 --> 06:54.040
Congratulations, congratulations.

06:54.040 --> 06:55.170
Did you invite them?

06:56.390 --> 06:57.480
Of course not.

06:57.680 --> 06:58.720
It must've been Wuyi.

06:58.720 --> 06:59.680
I didn't.

06:59.800 --> 07:00.480
Then...

07:00.800 --> 07:02.360
Father, don't worry about it.

07:02.360 --> 07:03.800
It's not every day
Wuyi throws such a grand affair.

07:03.800 --> 07:05.360
Of course they came to help him
make a good showing.

07:05.360 --> 07:08.110
His Highness Prince Qi has arrived!

07:08.870 --> 07:10.730
-Your Highness.
-Your Highness.

07:13.350 --> 07:14.410
Congratulations.

07:14.870 --> 07:15.870
I'm not late, am I?

07:16.600 --> 07:19.330
Your Highness has arrived
at just the right time.

07:20.310 --> 07:20.950
Thank you.

07:32.830 --> 07:33.680
From now on,

07:33.680 --> 07:35.159
we are no longer brothers,

07:37.830 --> 07:39.270
but ruler and subject.

07:45.810 --> 07:47.140
Who is beating the drum?

07:47.310 --> 07:49.040
This must be a grave injustice.

07:55.270 --> 07:57.159
Someone is sounding the Petition Drum.

07:57.159 --> 07:58.020
Petition Drum?

08:00.270 --> 08:01.070
It's struck only when the people

08:01.070 --> 08:01.920
have suffered a great injustice

08:01.920 --> 08:03.240
or when enemy forces are invading.

08:03.240 --> 08:05.300
Anyone who dares to strike that drum,

08:05.510 --> 08:07.040
whether their accusation is true or false,

08:07.040 --> 08:08.720
must first endure 30 strikes of the cane

08:08.720 --> 08:10.680
to prove they're not
making a false accusation.

08:10.680 --> 08:12.430
Wouldn't that leave them dead or crippled?

08:12.430 --> 08:14.560
Therefore, unless someone has
genuinely suffered a serious injustice,

08:14.560 --> 08:16.510
no one would risk their own life
like this.

08:16.510 --> 08:19.190
Something major
is about to happen at court.

08:23.640 --> 08:25.140
It has begun.

08:32.690 --> 08:33.380
My Lord!

08:34.390 --> 08:35.630
Who is it you intend to accuse?

08:35.630 --> 08:37.870
We accuse the Commander of the Beifu Army,

08:37.870 --> 08:40.240
the Heir of Prince Jing'an, Xiao Wuyi,

08:40.360 --> 08:42.720
and his brother, Xiao Yao,
supervisor of the grain canal works.

08:42.720 --> 08:43.320
What?

08:43.320 --> 08:45.790
My Lord, please seek justice for us!

08:57.390 --> 08:59.250
The auspicious hour has arrived.

09:08.960 --> 09:11.440
We respectfully invite Prince Qi,
the Regent, to bestow

09:11.440 --> 09:14.550
the imperial decree and seal upon
the Consort of the Heir of Prince Jing'an

09:14.550 --> 09:17.150
and read out
the proclamation of investiture.

09:26.360 --> 09:27.200
Report!

09:39.510 --> 09:42.040
Where are the accused,
Xiao Wuyi and Xiao Yao?

09:44.720 --> 09:46.790
I pay my respects to Your Highness.

09:46.790 --> 09:47.870
Your Highness,

09:47.960 --> 09:49.320
I have no wish to disrupt

09:49.320 --> 09:51.080
the Heir's Consort investiture ceremony.

09:51.080 --> 09:53.210
But the Petition Drum has been struck.

09:53.360 --> 09:54.670
According to the laws of Ye,

09:54.670 --> 09:56.670
the main culprits
must be detained immediately:

09:56.670 --> 09:59.240
Young Lord Xiao
and Eldest Young Master Xiao.

10:00.670 --> 10:02.240
Please forgive the offense.

10:02.240 --> 10:03.040
How insolent!

10:04.870 --> 10:06.550
Today, at the investiture ceremony,

10:06.550 --> 10:08.870
I'd like to see who dares arrest them!

10:09.830 --> 10:11.480
The Ministry of Justice never

10:11.480 --> 10:13.510
makes arrests without evidence.

10:13.870 --> 10:16.000
The grain canal in Hexi has collapsed,

10:16.000 --> 10:18.440
causing over 1,000 casualties
and public outrage.

10:18.440 --> 10:19.320
Our investigation found

10:19.320 --> 10:20.960
that County Magistrate Wei Min,
a man of humble birth,

10:20.960 --> 10:22.870
was personally promoted
by Young Lord Xiao.

10:22.870 --> 10:23.910
In his home,

10:23.910 --> 10:25.960
we found years of correspondence
between him

10:25.960 --> 10:27.750
and Young Lord Xiao
and Eldest Young Master Xiao,

10:27.750 --> 10:29.480
along with 1,000 taels of gold.

10:30.510 --> 10:32.360
Moreover, the letters reveal evidence

10:32.360 --> 10:34.360
that the Xiaos embezzled
the canal repair funds

10:34.360 --> 10:36.320
and abused their power for personal gain.

10:36.320 --> 10:38.920
Commandant of Justice,
if the sons are guilty,

10:39.160 --> 10:41.550
shouldn't the father be guilty as well?

10:42.350 --> 10:44.010
You may arrest the two of them,

10:44.340 --> 10:46.310
but you'll be taking me too!

10:47.150 --> 10:48.750
I'd like to see which of you dares!

10:48.750 --> 10:49.950
Take Prince Jing'an,

10:50.030 --> 10:52.160
the Heir, and Eldest Young Master Xiao

10:52.720 --> 10:55.050
to the Court of Judicial Review together.

10:55.240 --> 10:56.790
Yes, Your Highness.

10:57.550 --> 10:58.840
Order the Three Judicial Offices
to send officials

10:58.840 --> 11:01.670
to conduct a thorough investigation
at the grain canal.

11:01.670 --> 11:02.910
If they have been wronged,

11:02.910 --> 11:04.570
I will ensure justice is done.

11:06.550 --> 11:07.750
If they are guilty...

11:10.320 --> 11:12.400
I will never allow anyone

11:13.200 --> 11:14.870
to escape the law.

11:16.270 --> 11:18.800
Prince Jing'an,
please forgive the offense.

11:22.000 --> 11:24.000
Young Lord Xiao, please.

11:29.350 --> 11:31.760
Don't worry. I'll be back.

11:53.480 --> 11:56.280
Your Highness,
please bestow the decree and seal.

12:04.000 --> 12:07.000
Your Highness, please proceed with
the investiture.

12:21.240 --> 12:23.800
[Court of Judicial Review]

12:38.270 --> 12:40.240
Young Lord Xiao, you seem so composed.

12:40.240 --> 12:41.370
Are you that certain

12:42.240 --> 12:44.840
I won't find
conclusive evidence against you?

12:45.080 --> 12:46.720
There is a list in my residence

12:46.720 --> 12:47.600
recording every official

12:47.600 --> 12:48.720
who has ever attempted

12:48.720 --> 12:49.910
to bribe me.

12:50.630 --> 12:53.230
I've already sent a copy
to the Eastern Palace.

12:53.270 --> 12:56.000
Now I'll hand the original copy
of the list to you.

12:56.000 --> 12:57.440
If such a list really exists,

12:57.440 --> 12:58.750
why didn't you mention it earlier?

12:58.750 --> 13:00.210
Today, before the public,

13:00.510 --> 13:02.150
the Petition Drum has been struck,

13:02.150 --> 13:04.200
so you've come
bearing the will of the people.

13:04.200 --> 13:05.510
Whether the accusations are true or false,

13:05.510 --> 13:08.240
they must go through the Court of Judicial Review's process
to convince everyone.

13:08.240 --> 13:11.120
If I hadn't come,
it would've damaged your reputation.

13:11.120 --> 13:12.030
And by coming,

13:12.910 --> 13:14.840
I placed my bet on your competence.

13:15.080 --> 13:16.270
In that case,

13:16.270 --> 13:18.670
I should be thanking you, Young Lord Xiao?

13:18.670 --> 13:19.930
There is one more thing

13:20.320 --> 13:21.390
I'd ask you to consider,
Commandant of Justice.

13:21.390 --> 13:23.050
Please go on, Young Lord Xiao.

13:23.120 --> 13:25.390
I've long heard
that you're strict and impartial.

13:25.390 --> 13:27.120
However, my father is elderly,

13:27.320 --> 13:29.000
and my elder brother's leg
is badly crippled.

13:29.000 --> 13:30.390
Neither could endure torture.

13:30.390 --> 13:31.910
Moreover, every order
regarding the grain canal work

13:31.910 --> 13:33.120
was issued by me.

13:33.510 --> 13:34.840
If torture is to be used,

13:35.200 --> 13:36.630
I'm willing to endure it in their place.

13:36.630 --> 13:38.720
Xiao Wuyi, don't shield me!

13:39.240 --> 13:40.200
Since I dared to come in,

13:40.200 --> 13:41.640
I am not afraid of interrogation!

13:41.640 --> 13:43.300
What do you mean by "elderly"?

13:43.670 --> 13:45.750
I'm sturdier
than the two of them put together!

13:45.750 --> 13:47.280
Interrogate me if you must!

13:47.670 --> 13:48.910
Rest assured, everyone.

13:48.910 --> 13:50.790
If this turns out to be a frame-up,

13:50.980 --> 13:54.580
I will absolutely restore the good name of

13:54.750 --> 13:55.750
your household.

14:03.200 --> 14:04.130
I entered prison

14:04.910 --> 14:06.120
precisely to see

14:06.840 --> 14:08.000
just how far

14:08.240 --> 14:10.670
the person behind all this
is willing to go.

14:20.000 --> 14:20.630
Yuanji.

14:23.720 --> 14:24.960
Mother had some calming tonic

14:24.960 --> 14:25.960
and is asleep now.

14:28.080 --> 14:29.440
The letters and ledgers in the household

14:29.440 --> 14:30.640
have all been seized.

14:30.870 --> 14:31.960
Could it be that the Ministry of Justice

14:31.960 --> 14:32.870
has been acting under someone's orders,

14:32.870 --> 14:33.930
trying to frame us?

14:35.480 --> 14:36.410
I don't think so.

14:36.670 --> 14:38.080
Commandant of Justice Lu, who came today,

14:38.080 --> 14:39.740
was newly promoted last year.

14:39.870 --> 14:41.080
During these years of reform,

14:41.080 --> 14:42.000
while serving in the provinces,

14:42.000 --> 14:43.440
he punished commoners
who cheated in the marketplace

14:43.440 --> 14:45.030
and sentenced noble clans
who seized land by force alike.

14:45.030 --> 14:46.080
He's a ruthless but upright official

14:46.080 --> 14:48.000
who enforces the law without favor.

14:48.000 --> 14:50.120
Since he personally came to
make the arrest today,

14:50.120 --> 14:52.450
he surely wouldn't act without evidence.

14:52.720 --> 14:53.750
The plaintiffs

14:53.750 --> 14:55.360
accuse the Beifu Army of embezzling

14:55.360 --> 14:56.790
and taking bribes
during the canal repairs,

14:56.790 --> 14:57.750
and cutting corners on the work—

14:57.750 --> 14:59.630
which caused the grain canal to collapse

14:59.630 --> 15:00.720
and killed many conscripted laborers.

15:00.720 --> 15:02.050
Yao would never do that.

15:07.240 --> 15:09.360
Letters, ledgers...

15:12.030 --> 15:12.630
Nanxing.

15:13.150 --> 15:13.630
My Lady.

15:13.790 --> 15:15.630
You have a photographic memory
for the accounts.

15:15.630 --> 15:18.890
You've been helping me
with the accounts these past years.

15:21.870 --> 15:23.550
So help me reconstruct them.

15:25.480 --> 15:25.960
Yes.

15:29.360 --> 15:30.360
Ledgers...

15:31.360 --> 15:32.600
Letters...

15:34.550 --> 15:35.630
Handwriting...

15:41.080 --> 15:42.340
What's wrong, Yuanji?

15:45.120 --> 15:45.720
Nothing.

15:46.410 --> 15:47.810
I just suddenly realized

15:48.150 --> 15:50.550
I haven't seen
Qing Long and Yan Yue around.

15:50.960 --> 15:52.840
Right, where are they?

15:56.550 --> 15:58.950
Xiao Wuyi and Xiao Ju
have been imprisoned.

15:59.240 --> 16:01.670
Have you prepared

16:01.870 --> 16:04.070
the forged correspondence I asked for?

16:10.360 --> 16:11.760
Afraid it'll be exposed?

16:14.080 --> 16:15.210
For the Xiao family,

16:16.270 --> 16:17.390
this will be a capital offense.

16:17.390 --> 16:20.150
They deserve it.

16:21.790 --> 16:23.720
I won't go back on my promise to you.

16:24.270 --> 16:26.800
I've already requested
Prince Qi's approval

16:27.030 --> 16:28.830
to reopen the Lantai gathering.

16:29.030 --> 16:29.790
Get up first.

16:30.450 --> 16:31.020
Come on.

16:35.080 --> 16:35.870
Zhaolin,

16:37.150 --> 16:38.410
when the time comes...

16:39.870 --> 16:42.550
you'll be a student of mine,

16:42.790 --> 16:44.240
and no one will ever

16:44.600 --> 16:46.600
look down on your background again.

16:52.550 --> 16:53.150
Thank you,

16:54.910 --> 16:55.840
Grand Tutor Xie.

17:02.720 --> 17:04.069
Are those people

17:04.920 --> 17:06.510
helping you cook the books

17:07.400 --> 17:08.400
actually trustworthy?

17:08.400 --> 17:09.200
They don't know

17:09.200 --> 17:10.329
what they're doing,

17:10.680 --> 17:12.750
nor do they know who they're working for.

17:12.750 --> 17:13.510
Excellent.

17:42.270 --> 17:43.200
Are you alright?

17:48.160 --> 17:48.690
Let's go!

17:54.510 --> 17:55.100
Hurry.

18:03.270 --> 18:04.110
Mr. Liu,

18:05.160 --> 18:08.020
since when did you become
Grand Tutor Xie's lackey?

18:10.480 --> 18:12.260
You knew I collected rare books.

18:12.260 --> 18:14.060
Xiao Yao, Xiao Wuyi,

18:14.510 --> 18:17.790
and even Prince Jing'an had
all borrowed and annotated them.

18:17.790 --> 18:20.070
So you used me to obtain

18:20.440 --> 18:22.240
the handwriting of every member

18:22.310 --> 18:24.840
of the Xiao family
by borrowing books from me.

18:25.770 --> 18:28.860
Back then, when you gave me
a deed of debt...

18:29.340 --> 18:30.670
I offer this deed of debt

18:31.030 --> 18:31.920
as proof

18:32.720 --> 18:34.230
that I'll surely repay the debt someday.

18:34.230 --> 18:36.150
When you said
you'd repay me for saving your life,

18:36.150 --> 18:37.750
you'd already thought of
how you could use me?

18:37.750 --> 18:39.510
Absolutely not! I...

18:42.680 --> 18:43.790
I admire you.

18:46.110 --> 18:47.710
But I didn't dare to tell you.

18:51.830 --> 18:52.920
I knew all along.

18:54.640 --> 18:57.900
I've frequented the bookstore
these past couple of years.

18:59.240 --> 19:00.780
Could you really not tell
how I felt about you?

19:00.780 --> 19:02.440
It's precisely because I know

19:02.670 --> 19:05.200
that I'm even more aware
I'm not worthy of you.

19:05.480 --> 19:06.750
Whether you were the Consort of the Heir
of Prince Jing'an back then

19:06.750 --> 19:07.960
or are the head of the He family now,

19:07.960 --> 19:09.360
I was never worthy of you.

19:11.550 --> 19:12.720
I'm merely a commoner,

19:12.720 --> 19:13.880
full of ideals.

19:14.240 --> 19:15.640
Anyone can trample on me.

19:16.200 --> 19:17.400
Only Grand Tutor Xie.

19:18.200 --> 19:19.060
He promised me.

19:19.400 --> 19:20.800
As long as Xiao Wuyi falls

19:20.960 --> 19:23.590
and the noble clans
revive the Lantai gathering,

19:23.590 --> 19:25.320
he'll give me an official post.

19:36.850 --> 19:38.980
You're the third child in your family.

19:39.310 --> 19:41.240
You once studied at Luming Academy

19:42.240 --> 19:44.700
and were classmates
with my second brother.

19:45.270 --> 19:46.310
Back then,

19:46.900 --> 19:49.350
I often secretly put on
my second brother's clothes

19:49.350 --> 19:52.150
and sneaked into the academy
to sit in on lectures.

19:52.240 --> 19:54.170
We got to know each other over time.

19:54.690 --> 19:56.290
We shared the same interests

19:56.510 --> 19:58.110
and often studied together.

19:58.750 --> 20:00.880
It was only then that my brother told you

20:00.880 --> 20:02.120
I was actually a girl.

20:02.930 --> 20:04.660
You were shocked yet delighted

20:05.030 --> 20:08.310
and said you'd return home and ask
your parents to arrange our marriage.

20:08.310 --> 20:09.720
But just at that time,

20:10.270 --> 20:11.870
my aunt, Empress Dowager He,

20:11.880 --> 20:13.440
was choosing someone from the clan

20:13.440 --> 20:15.120
to marry into Prince Jing'an's household.

20:15.120 --> 20:16.520
But I was in love with you.

20:16.880 --> 20:18.210
After my aunt found out,

20:18.310 --> 20:19.840
she sent people to kill you.

20:25.830 --> 20:26.790
I thought

20:27.750 --> 20:28.880
you were dead.

20:31.030 --> 20:32.160
But I never imagined

20:34.480 --> 20:36.080
that day at the bookstore...

20:36.350 --> 20:37.350
Pei Runheng?

20:40.030 --> 20:41.680
I'd see you again.

20:43.830 --> 20:44.640
Impossible.

20:46.960 --> 20:48.400
You definitely got the wrong person.

20:48.400 --> 20:50.460
You were born in the Year of the Tiger.

20:51.550 --> 20:54.830
There's a plum blossom-shaped scar
on your left arm.

20:56.750 --> 21:00.200
You got it when you were protecting me
from wild bees while we were

21:00.200 --> 21:03.330
picking mulberries in the back mountain
of the academy.

21:04.400 --> 21:05.660
And your handwriting.

21:08.270 --> 21:09.670
I would never mistake it.

21:12.960 --> 21:14.920
Then why didn't you tell me sooner?

21:18.110 --> 21:21.030
In the second year after I married into
Prince Jing'an's household,

21:21.030 --> 21:23.240
Empress Dowager He found a pretext

21:23.440 --> 21:24.970
and convicted your family.

21:25.750 --> 21:27.480
Your father and brothers died,

21:27.590 --> 21:30.070
and your mother, in her despair,
took her own life along with your sister.

21:30.070 --> 21:31.800
I'm a daughter of the He family.

21:32.030 --> 21:34.760
Our families have long been
bound by a blood feud.

21:34.880 --> 21:37.080
I didn't dare let you remember the past.

21:37.720 --> 21:39.380
I foolishly convinced myself

21:40.480 --> 21:42.410
that as long as I didn't speak of it,

21:42.510 --> 21:45.720
we could have a fresh start together.

21:46.550 --> 21:47.880
But I never expected...

21:49.720 --> 21:50.270
I never expected

21:50.270 --> 21:52.600
you to be deceived
and used by Xie Huaigui.

21:53.440 --> 21:57.480
Runheng, you can still turn back now.

22:01.640 --> 22:02.970
My right hand is ruined.

22:03.880 --> 22:05.070
I can no longer prove

22:05.070 --> 22:07.680
that those letters and ledgers
were forged by me.

22:07.680 --> 22:09.070
You are living proof.

22:11.160 --> 22:12.000
Jiayu.

22:23.750 --> 22:27.880
What exactly is the crime Grand Tutor Xie
intends to pin on the Xiao family?

22:28.010 --> 22:28.860
Treason...

22:33.920 --> 22:35.850
and collaboration with the enemy.

22:44.270 --> 22:46.720
Tell us everything you know.

22:48.680 --> 22:49.680
At this point,

22:50.270 --> 22:50.960
Runheng,

22:51.400 --> 22:53.600
for the sake of the person you once were,

22:53.640 --> 22:55.440
don't keep going down this road.

23:07.270 --> 23:08.800
Third Alley, Shanghe Ward.

23:09.830 --> 23:11.680
The scholars who forged
the letters and ledgers

23:11.680 --> 23:12.880
are all hidden there.

23:13.240 --> 23:14.240
If you move quickly,

23:14.240 --> 23:16.640
you might still be able to
save some of them.

23:20.680 --> 23:21.790
Too late again.

23:37.030 --> 23:38.760
The outcome is not yet decided.

23:40.350 --> 23:42.480
Prince Qi, don't you think
you've come a little early?

23:42.480 --> 23:43.610
These past few days,

23:43.960 --> 23:45.760
the evidence has been piling up—

23:45.830 --> 23:47.790
Xiao Yao's corruption
in the grain canal project,

23:47.790 --> 23:50.350
and Xiao Ju's sale of military supplies
and leaking of military intelligence.

23:50.350 --> 23:51.640
Not just your family—

23:51.750 --> 23:54.300
many of the common-born officials
you promoted

23:54.300 --> 23:55.960
have been dragged down with you as well.

23:55.960 --> 23:59.310
Now, the public in and out of Jiankang
is outraged,

24:00.030 --> 24:03.350
demanding severe punishment
for your family

24:03.480 --> 24:06.070
and a strict investigation
of common-born officials.

24:06.070 --> 24:09.000
Do you think you still have a way out,

24:10.920 --> 24:12.640
Crown Prince Wenxi?

24:21.070 --> 24:24.310
From the day His Majesty returned
the Phoenix Heart Token to you,

24:24.310 --> 24:26.040
I was certain of your identity.

24:26.880 --> 24:28.740
From supervising the grain canal

24:30.000 --> 24:32.000
to charges of treason, it's exactly

24:32.920 --> 24:36.650
the same pattern as the downfall
of the An and Lu families back then.

24:38.240 --> 24:41.370
Grand Tutor Xie has certainly
put a great deal of thought

24:43.110 --> 24:45.370
into choosing the Xiao family's crimes.

24:47.880 --> 24:50.810
So you really do know
the truth behind the An-Lu case.

24:51.000 --> 24:52.110
And since you know,

24:52.440 --> 24:53.440
you should also realize

24:53.440 --> 24:55.920
that Grand Tutor Xie isn't
leaving you any way out.

24:55.920 --> 24:57.270
Xie Jiayu acted fast

24:57.680 --> 25:00.550
and found the one
who forged the letters and ledgers.

25:00.550 --> 25:02.070
But that man's hand is ruined.

25:02.070 --> 25:03.070
He can't testify.

25:05.350 --> 25:07.680
For the sake of our past brotherhood,

25:08.750 --> 25:10.400
I can spare your whole family...

25:10.400 --> 25:13.530
I won't agree to the conditions
you're about to propose.

25:17.550 --> 25:19.790
Hand over the Beifu Army
and the Phoenix Heart Token,

25:19.790 --> 25:21.520
and write a divorce agreement.

25:21.920 --> 25:23.960
I want you to tell Xie Jiayu yourself

25:23.960 --> 25:25.560
that you want to divorce her.

25:27.550 --> 25:29.750
Do you honestly think that's possible?

25:46.240 --> 25:47.440
I think it is.

25:55.980 --> 25:58.250
Xie Jiayu is her own person.

25:58.830 --> 25:59.960
Her life

26:01.030 --> 26:02.200
and her feelings

26:03.310 --> 26:05.110
should be hers to choose.

26:06.480 --> 26:08.440
You're forcing her to come back to you—

26:08.440 --> 26:10.070
is it because you love her

26:12.000 --> 26:14.160
or because you hate me?

26:14.180 --> 26:17.040
That was Xie Jiayu's own wrong choice
to begin with.

26:18.270 --> 26:19.240
I'm merely giving her

26:19.240 --> 26:20.920
a chance to choose again.

26:27.160 --> 26:28.070
Li Yizhi.

26:31.440 --> 26:33.840
You shouldn't have dragged the Xiao family

26:34.070 --> 26:36.730
and all those common-born officials
into this.

26:39.310 --> 26:41.920
Do you really think
all those commoners you promoted

26:41.920 --> 26:44.450
are people of
both talent and good character?

26:46.550 --> 26:49.400
Cruel and corrupt officials
mostly come from humble origins.

26:49.400 --> 26:52.250
The common people have long since grown
to despise the reforms.

26:52.250 --> 26:55.510
Even if everything you've done
was meant to save the realm,

26:55.890 --> 26:56.810
then tell me—

26:57.310 --> 27:00.750
how many people can
truly understand your intentions?

27:01.510 --> 27:04.040
And how many
would actually appreciate them?

27:04.680 --> 27:06.880
All you'll get is more and more people

27:07.880 --> 27:09.830
wanting you dead.

27:18.830 --> 27:20.110
And you don't fully know

27:20.110 --> 27:21.700
this father of yours either.

27:21.700 --> 27:23.560
Xiao Ju was not dragged into this.

27:24.310 --> 27:25.790
He and your birth mother

27:26.230 --> 27:29.090
were both perpetrators
of the An-Lu wrongful case.

27:29.920 --> 27:31.350
He's selfish and cowardly

27:31.350 --> 27:34.750
and will abandon all moral principles
for his own interests.

27:35.680 --> 27:37.410
The downfall of the Xiao family

27:37.480 --> 27:38.480
is inevitable.

27:39.160 --> 27:41.360
If you really want to protect Xie Jiayu,

27:42.000 --> 27:46.070
divorce is the only path left.

28:06.510 --> 28:08.920
The grain canal collapsed,
the Xiao family embezzled,

28:08.920 --> 28:13.050
Xiao Wuyi was imprisoned, and the ruler
and his subject became estranged.

28:13.680 --> 28:14.740
You're very smart.

28:15.310 --> 28:17.350
You know that the truth of the An-Lu case

28:17.350 --> 28:19.150
is Xie Huaigui's real obsession

28:19.550 --> 28:20.750
and that if he learns

28:21.070 --> 28:23.000
Xiao Ju knew of the injustice back then

28:23.000 --> 28:24.070
yet concealed it,

28:24.680 --> 28:26.680
he will never let the Xiao family go.

28:31.680 --> 28:33.410
Xiao Wuyi has been imprisoned.

28:33.830 --> 28:34.790
Are you happy?

28:39.160 --> 28:40.270
If he dies,

28:40.590 --> 28:42.550
Xie Jiayu will be left
without anyone to rely on.

28:42.550 --> 28:45.280
Your brother is now the Regent
in name and in fact.

28:45.510 --> 28:47.440
You can also return to Southern Ye.

28:57.960 --> 28:58.960
I belong

28:59.790 --> 29:01.250
to you now, Your Highness.

29:02.070 --> 29:04.510
And I'll never go back in this life.

29:05.090 --> 29:06.950
Without Xiao Wuyi, the Beifu Army

29:07.110 --> 29:08.770
has lost its fighting spirit.

29:09.350 --> 29:12.830
It'll never again be a match
for Your Highness's Black Eagle Army.

29:12.830 --> 29:14.960
From now on, the border will be secure.

29:15.680 --> 29:18.480
I should congratulate Your Highness.

29:19.750 --> 29:20.590
Is that so?

29:21.550 --> 29:24.640
You're helping your brother
eliminate his greatest rival,

29:24.640 --> 29:27.300
and yet you still find
such a pretty way to put it.

29:29.310 --> 29:30.170
Your Highness,

29:30.480 --> 29:32.110
all the warriors participating in
today's mounted archery contest

29:32.110 --> 29:32.910
have arrived.

29:33.270 --> 29:35.440
The cattle, sheep, and Ye slaves
have also been brought into the arena.

29:35.440 --> 29:36.200
I know.

29:38.070 --> 29:40.200
Then let me help Your Highness change.

29:48.590 --> 29:49.200
Lejun.

29:57.480 --> 29:58.280
What's wrong?

29:58.790 --> 29:59.830
My child...

30:00.680 --> 30:01.710
Our child?

30:03.300 --> 30:04.630
You did this on purpose.

30:04.840 --> 30:05.970
You didn't want him.

30:06.400 --> 30:08.330
You didn't want our child, did you?

30:09.680 --> 30:10.270
I...

30:11.510 --> 30:12.590
didn't...

30:18.000 --> 30:19.610
Lejun. Lejun!

30:25.510 --> 30:27.030
We were still a step too late.

30:27.030 --> 30:28.920
We only have Liu Zhaolin as a witness,

30:28.920 --> 30:30.360
but his hand is ruined.

30:30.920 --> 30:32.510
I'm afraid his testimony alone
won't convince anyone.

30:32.510 --> 30:33.240
Not too late.

30:33.320 --> 30:35.320
At least now we know who's behind it.

30:35.350 --> 30:36.000
Jiayu.

30:38.270 --> 30:39.330
There is something

30:39.830 --> 30:40.960
you need to know now.

30:44.160 --> 30:46.030
If Xiao Wuyi
keeps pushing himself like this,

30:46.030 --> 30:47.560
he probably won't even last

30:48.240 --> 30:49.170
another year.

30:53.160 --> 30:55.420
Xiao Wuyi didn't mean to keep it from you.

31:04.480 --> 31:05.510
Then how is he

31:06.510 --> 31:07.240
now?

31:09.040 --> 31:10.300
It's well controlled.

31:10.520 --> 31:12.850
In enclosed spaces
or in the dark at night,

31:12.880 --> 31:13.720
it worsens.

31:14.380 --> 31:16.180
But he's learned to live with it.

31:17.770 --> 31:19.140
What worries me most now

31:19.200 --> 31:22.200
is that the Court of Judicial Review
will use torture.

31:22.400 --> 31:23.550
I heard from Yuanji

31:23.570 --> 31:25.310
that Commandant of Justice Lu
is a harsh official.

31:25.310 --> 31:27.370
If Xiao Wuyi's condition worsens...

31:28.400 --> 31:30.030
there's no telling what will happen.

31:30.030 --> 31:32.430
For now, the priority is finding a way
to get him out

31:32.430 --> 31:33.560
as soon as possible.

31:35.970 --> 31:38.820
[Grand Tutor's Mansion]

31:38.870 --> 31:40.930
[Xie]

31:42.350 --> 31:44.220
Third Alley, Shanghe Ward
has been emptied.

31:44.220 --> 31:46.750
Grand Tutor Xie,
you've fabricated charges.

31:47.640 --> 31:49.480
You framed the Beifu Army commander
who bled

31:49.480 --> 31:51.880
for this nation as a traitor
who colluded with the enemy.

31:51.880 --> 31:53.680
When you wake in the middle of the night,

31:53.680 --> 31:56.080
doesn't your conscience ever trouble you?

31:59.960 --> 32:01.560
Yaoyao, you're thoughtful.

32:04.170 --> 32:05.610
A troubled conscience?

32:09.460 --> 32:12.060
I'm only doing to him
what he once did to others.

32:16.680 --> 32:17.480
You mean...

32:18.790 --> 32:20.680
Prince Jing'an framed
the An and Lu families?

32:20.680 --> 32:22.790
He knew there was an injustice
in the An-Lu case,

32:22.790 --> 32:23.920
yet he concealed it.

32:24.070 --> 32:26.270
How is that any different from framing?

32:26.350 --> 32:27.480
And Xiao Wuyi.

32:28.510 --> 32:30.240
Since he is Crown Prince Wenxi,

32:30.350 --> 32:31.640
he naturally must atone for

32:31.640 --> 32:33.900
the sins committed by his birth parents.

32:42.000 --> 32:44.750
Yaoyao, concocting an unjust case

32:45.350 --> 32:48.110
might be unfair to others,

32:48.400 --> 32:49.710
but to the Xiao family

32:49.880 --> 32:51.590
and Crown Prince Wenxi,

32:52.830 --> 32:54.110
it's Heaven's will.

32:55.030 --> 32:57.550
Heaven's justice always comes full circle—

32:58.070 --> 32:59.270
this is retribution.

33:02.880 --> 33:03.510
Father.

33:05.680 --> 33:06.880
What really happened

33:07.480 --> 33:09.410
to the An and Lu families back then?

33:13.310 --> 33:17.110
Just as the Xiao family is
experiencing today.

33:17.280 --> 33:20.090
[Prince Jing'an's Mansion]

33:20.830 --> 33:21.590
My Lady, how did you know

33:21.590 --> 33:24.250
about the mechanism
in Grand Tutor Xie's study?

33:25.070 --> 33:26.110
I was mischievous as a child

33:26.110 --> 33:28.370
and stumbled upon
the mechanism by accident.

33:28.370 --> 33:30.570
You know what's inside the box, My Lady?

33:31.590 --> 33:32.270
No.

33:32.440 --> 33:35.570
But they must be extremely important
to Grand Tutor Xie.

33:35.920 --> 33:37.960
Qizhou, Qingzhou...

33:38.440 --> 33:39.350
And Luzhou.

33:41.550 --> 33:42.480
Where did you go?

33:42.830 --> 33:44.070
After His Highness was imprisoned,

33:44.070 --> 33:46.120
Qing Long and I were ordered to
go to Luzhou to find someone.

33:46.120 --> 33:46.680
Who?

33:46.960 --> 33:50.070
Prince Qi's adoptive mother,
Madam Wang of the Lu family.

33:50.070 --> 33:52.270
Originally, she'd always been
under His Highness's control,

33:52.270 --> 33:53.920
but she was poisoned at some point.

33:53.920 --> 33:55.070
We were still a step too late.

33:55.070 --> 33:56.270
A step too late again.

33:56.720 --> 33:58.000
Actually, Her Highness Princess Yunzhao

33:58.000 --> 33:59.860
also sent me to these three places

33:59.880 --> 34:01.510
to look for Madam Wang of the Lu family.

34:01.510 --> 34:03.920
It was shortly after
Prince Qi was appointed Regent.

34:03.920 --> 34:04.880
That's also why

34:05.160 --> 34:07.760
I didn't go to Lingfeng Fort
with Her Highness.

34:09.560 --> 34:11.219
What did Mother send you to do?

34:11.850 --> 34:14.250
To investigate Prince Qi's true identity.

34:14.510 --> 34:16.510
For Mao, for our family,

34:16.880 --> 34:19.679
you must be this pawn.

34:20.920 --> 34:22.280
I finally understand

34:23.440 --> 34:24.969
why Lejun killed my mother,

34:25.630 --> 34:26.840
why my father and mother

34:26.840 --> 34:28.500
divorced after I got married,

34:29.840 --> 34:31.030
and why my mother never approved

34:31.030 --> 34:32.630
of Mao and me being together.

34:36.190 --> 34:37.520
I understand it all now.

34:40.920 --> 34:43.210
[Shezhang Hall]

34:49.070 --> 34:51.280
I, Xie Jiayu,
Consort of the Heir of Prince Jing'an,

34:51.280 --> 34:53.139
pay respects to Regent Prince Qi.

34:59.670 --> 35:00.670
Let her in.

35:11.150 --> 35:12.960
The corruption and treason of

35:13.280 --> 35:16.080
Prince Jing'an's family
have all been confirmed.

35:18.280 --> 35:20.360
No matter how badly you want to save him,

35:20.360 --> 35:22.670
Xiao Wuyi has no other choice

35:23.230 --> 35:25.690
but to hand over
the command of the Beifu Army

35:25.710 --> 35:27.150
and write a confession.

35:27.230 --> 35:28.000
I came today

35:28.480 --> 35:29.740
to give you something.

35:35.830 --> 35:37.510
[Li Mao's Lineage Investigation]

35:50.840 --> 35:52.800
Xiao Wuyi has known
your true identity all along.

35:52.800 --> 35:54.330
If he wanted your position,

35:54.760 --> 35:56.420
it would've been his long ago.

35:58.070 --> 35:59.400
You trust him that much?

36:00.230 --> 36:02.030
The facts speak for themselves,

36:02.110 --> 36:03.910
whether you believe them or not.

36:08.250 --> 36:10.000
And if I keep you here,

36:11.360 --> 36:12.620
then all this evidence

36:14.480 --> 36:15.650
will mean nothing.

36:19.400 --> 36:20.730
Yaoyao, don't force me.

36:21.450 --> 36:23.300
I'm not the Li Mao I used to be.

36:24.090 --> 36:25.840
If I can't get what I want,

36:25.840 --> 36:27.640
then we'll all go down together.

36:30.320 --> 36:31.980
I'll give you one last chance.

36:33.230 --> 36:35.230
Take off those robes
of the Heir's Consort,

36:35.230 --> 36:36.230
leave Xiao Wuyi,

36:36.570 --> 36:38.100
and stay by my side forever.

36:39.390 --> 36:40.150
Okay?

36:48.430 --> 36:49.110
No.

36:50.110 --> 36:53.280
I also have the letters
exchanged between Grand Tutor Xie

36:53.280 --> 36:55.340
and your wet nurse
over the past dozen years.

36:55.340 --> 36:56.780
He still doesn't know

36:57.280 --> 36:58.610
that I took the letters.

36:59.320 --> 37:00.720
I'll give you three days.

37:01.000 --> 37:02.200
If, after three days,

37:02.330 --> 37:04.400
Wuyi and the rest of the Xiao family
have not returned

37:04.400 --> 37:07.180
and if the Court of Judicial Review
has not cleared their name,

37:07.180 --> 37:09.380
then this record of your true identity,

37:10.320 --> 37:11.960
along with the letters
between the Grand Tutor

37:11.960 --> 37:14.000
and your wet nurse
over the past dozen years,

37:14.000 --> 37:16.060
will be spread throughout Jiankang.

37:22.590 --> 37:23.360
Mao,

37:24.630 --> 37:26.710
whether I'm the Heir's Consort or not,

37:26.710 --> 37:27.910
I'm still Xie Jiayu.

37:28.480 --> 37:30.340
Whether I'm with Xiao Wuyi or not,

37:31.070 --> 37:33.470
I won't choose to
enter the palace with you.

37:34.760 --> 37:37.230
These past few years,
I've traveled to many places

37:37.230 --> 37:38.560
and lived very happily.

37:39.840 --> 37:41.500
Don't stay trapped in the past

37:41.960 --> 37:43.820
and let it become your obsession.

37:45.650 --> 37:47.580
You were never this kind of person.

38:05.110 --> 38:08.550
[Court of Judicial Review]

38:29.510 --> 38:30.550
Yaoyao came.

38:34.150 --> 38:35.510
When did you

38:36.260 --> 38:38.260
start suspecting my true identity?

38:40.150 --> 38:43.670
From the moment Prince Changsha
mutinied to force the abdication

38:43.670 --> 38:46.680
and you were suddenly pushed to
the position of Regent.

38:46.680 --> 38:47.470
I thought

38:48.320 --> 38:51.380
it was at least
after Lejun got rid of Princess Yunzhao.

38:51.840 --> 38:53.900
I didn't expect it to be even earlier.

38:54.840 --> 38:55.670
That night,

38:57.070 --> 38:59.030
when I saw you in Jiankang Palace,

38:59.280 --> 39:00.210
I was wondering:

39:00.880 --> 39:02.190
Grand Tutor Xie had been plotting
for a long time,

39:02.190 --> 39:04.270
so why did he choose you specifically?

39:04.270 --> 39:05.310
As expected,

39:06.580 --> 39:08.920
His Majesty immediately
sent people to Qizhou

39:08.920 --> 39:10.920
to investigate your true identity.

39:11.710 --> 39:14.170
Princess Yunzhao's Shadow Envoys also went

39:14.550 --> 39:17.010
and found out the truth
they shouldn't have.

39:17.030 --> 39:19.320
But at that time, why didn't you...

39:19.320 --> 39:20.670
Why didn't I expose you

39:21.320 --> 39:24.250
and make this crime
of deceiving the emperor public?

39:31.550 --> 39:33.810
Because you and I have the same ambition.

39:35.150 --> 39:36.610
What I cannot accomplish,

39:37.480 --> 39:39.210
you can accomplish in my place.

39:40.400 --> 39:41.920
I don't need an incompetent good man

39:41.920 --> 39:43.450
standing in that position.

39:43.880 --> 39:45.730
Ambition, ruthless methods—

39:45.760 --> 39:47.690
whoever holds that position needs both.

39:47.690 --> 39:50.820
I don't think
there's anything wrong with your origins.

39:55.000 --> 39:56.800
You don't care about the throne,

39:57.910 --> 39:59.580
but you need a helper.

40:00.550 --> 40:02.230
So you chose me.

40:04.320 --> 40:05.630
For your ambition,

40:05.630 --> 40:06.800
I lost Yaoyao.

40:06.800 --> 40:08.660
I lost the life I was meant to have!

40:11.280 --> 40:13.140
I am not willing to be your puppet,

40:16.030 --> 40:18.670
and even less willing to accept
that Yaoyao remains so devoted to you.

40:18.670 --> 40:20.590
She loves freedom more than anything,

40:20.590 --> 40:22.400
yet she's willing to be bound to your side

40:22.400 --> 40:24.000
and give everything for you!

40:35.590 --> 40:38.920
Those noble clans thought
that making peace with Northern Qin

40:38.920 --> 40:41.320
could buy a corner
of peace and prosperity.

40:42.000 --> 40:46.130
But that's only a fleeting prosperity
confined within Jiankang's walls.

40:46.320 --> 40:47.360
Beyond the city,

40:47.480 --> 40:48.550
countless people on the Northern Border

40:48.550 --> 40:50.000
still live amid war.

40:54.360 --> 40:55.550
If we don't eliminate Northern Qin

40:55.550 --> 40:56.440
and reclaim our lost homeland,

40:56.440 --> 40:58.100
there can never be true peace!

40:58.630 --> 40:59.280
Yizhi,

41:00.100 --> 41:01.550
these were your own words

41:01.550 --> 41:03.150
while you were fleeing here.

41:03.800 --> 41:05.550
It was you who forgot.

41:16.630 --> 41:17.960
The person who chose you

41:19.790 --> 41:20.650
was never me...

41:25.360 --> 41:26.760
but yourself.
